#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Update the Lambda"
msgstr "更新 Lambda"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can update the Java code as you see fit.  Once you've rebuilt, you can redeploy your lambda by executing the\n"
